{"data":[{"id":563771171,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b53af4e6943aa6c0e3651512f5c13b89","url_token":"yang-yi-66-95","name":"杨溢","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/8e6a1213f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/8e6a1213f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b53af4e6943aa6c0e3651512f5c13b89","user_type":"people","headline":"FGA，有专利，攻读地质学，曾涉猎生物学、化学，业余于经济学。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":83,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563771171","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-25f978784c2d09429687116f0ae75d7b_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275003,"updated_time":1546281271,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"comment_count":6,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e他不但不是天才，而且不是地才。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（原证明稿已被作者删除，2019.01.01, 01:58补充截图方便大家奇文共赏）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e民科们的成果不是名气大就能让质量变好的。曾经轰动一时的王洪成水变油事件，其相关的专利申请\u003cb\u003e全文\u003c/b\u003e见下图。稍有常识的人们都知道，该申请文件不但没有充分公开，而且没有创造性实用性新颖性，不能授予专利权。仅就发明专利而言，常见的高质量申请文件至少要有二十页的图文才能描述详尽，王洪成的所有文本加起来仅仅薄薄的一页，高下立判。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ed8eb723d7e52013280bf5e27d6f8cb_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1700\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-be0923cd7c97b1a71147dfd2684ea8ad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1700\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ed8eb723d7e52013280bf5e27d6f8cb_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1700'%20height='960'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1700\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-be0923cd7c97b1a71147dfd2684ea8ad_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1700\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ed8eb723d7e52013280bf5e27d6f8cb_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ed8eb723d7e52013280bf5e27d6f8cb_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e类似地，哥德巴赫猜想“1+1”相关的完备描述或证明，绝大多数情况不是本问题所述的四页纸（见下面四图）可以做到的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f6fa0920cb4dae8359434784b2c11361_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1334\" data-rawheight=\"1717\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5811cf19b526ae0f5a98bf7650f0f726_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1334\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f6fa0920cb4dae8359434784b2c11361_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1334'%20height='1717'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1334\" data-rawheight=\"1717\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5811cf19b526ae0f5a98bf7650f0f726_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1334\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f6fa0920cb4dae8359434784b2c11361_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f6fa0920cb4dae8359434784b2c11361_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-062197f998ab38f4e1b9bf3b9a139581_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1435\" data-rawheight=\"1746\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-362c3606cbb3017cadfc3f47a0c4a0f8_b.jpg